Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:45.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}独自流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:53.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无法对人微笑的我们
