Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:18.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}对悲伤挥手告别
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.93,0:23:20.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}然后  总有一天
